      <title>马克龙和肖尔茨组成统一阵线应对特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/macron-scholz-project-united-front-in-face-of-trump-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对唐纳德·特朗普总统破坏跨大西洋关系的威胁，埃马纽埃尔·马克龙和奥拉夫·朔尔茨周三呼吁欧洲团结起来，打造更强大、更具竞争力的欧洲工业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/macron-scholz-project-united-front-in-face-of-trump-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰部长称愿意帮助保险公司投资国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/dutch-willing-to-help-insurers-invest-in-defense-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长鲁本·布雷克曼斯表示，荷兰保险公司和其他希望投资国防工业的金融机构可以期待政府的指导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/dutch-willing-to-help-insurers-invest-in-defense-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求普京就乌克兰问题“达成协议”，否则将面临新的代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-tells-putin-to-make-a-deal-on-ukraine-or-face-new-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普加大对俄罗斯的压力，要求其通过谈判结束乌克兰战争，并威胁说，如果俄罗斯拒绝迅速结束战争，将对俄罗斯实施经济处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-tells-putin-to-make-a-deal-on-ukraine-or-face-new-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统拉马福萨与特朗普达成共识</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-sees-common-ground-with-dealmaker-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，他希望与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普找到共同点，尽管一些世界领导人对他重返白宫可能带来的后果感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-sees-common-ground-with-dealmaker-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚人逃离游击恐怖袭击 委内瑞拉战机飞越边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/venezuelan-jets-buzz-border-as-colombians-flee-guerrilla-terror</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉派出俄制军用飞机在边境巡逻，因为数万人逃离了哥伦比亚自 2016 年和平协议以来最严重的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/venezuelan-jets-buzz-border-as-colombians-flee-guerrilla-terror</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果美阿协议需要，米莱将退出区域贸易集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/milei-would-leave-mercosur-if-needed-for-us-argentina-trade-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱表示，如果有必要，他将退出南方共同市场，以巩固与美国的自由贸易协定，但他希望无需采取如此激烈的行动就能达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/milei-would-leave-mercosur-if-needed-for-us-argentina-trade-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:27:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典总理称 Northvolt 为欧洲提供了教训</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/swedish-premier-says-northvolt-teaches-lessons-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典首相乌尔夫·克里斯特松 (Ulf Kristersson) 表示，在电池制造商 Northvolt AB 倒闭后，需要重新思考欧洲政府和私营企业的合作方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/swedish-premier-says-northvolt-teaches-lessons-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 16:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战威胁加拿大银行股上涨 27% 后的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trade-war-labor-market-threaten-rally-in-canadian-banks-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大国家银行的分析师表示，加拿大银行股的上涨受到潜在贸易战的风险，贸易战将迅速导致失业率飙升和贷款违约率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trade-war-labor-market-threaten-rally-in-canadian-banks-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 15:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称美国必须成为乌克兰维和部队的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-news-zelenskiy-says-ukraine-needs-us-troops-to-secure-peace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基在与俄罗斯会谈前向唐纳德·特朗普发出呼吁，称任何在乌克兰部署的有效维和部队都需要包括美军。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-news-zelenskiy-says-ukraine-needs-us-troops-to-secure-peace</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 15:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰研究电缆泄露原因 质疑破坏行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/finland-s-stubb-says-baltic-sea-cable-breach-probe-remains-open</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰总统亚历山大·斯塔布表示，目前尚无定论，认为近期波罗的海海底电缆屡屡遭损毁是否为人为破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/finland-s-stubb-says-baltic-sea-cable-breach-probe-remains-open</guid>
